<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Booking Reminder - IpTruck</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .reminder-type {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #27ae60;
        }
        .details {
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #d1ecf1;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid #0c5460;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>ðŸ“… Booking Reminder</h1>
        <p>Your scheduled <%= reminderType %> is approaching</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello <%= contactPerson %>,</h2>
        
        <div class="highlight">
            <h3>ðŸš› Upcoming <%= reminderType %></h3>
            <p>We wanted to remind you that your scheduled <strong><%= reminderType %></strong> for booking <strong>#<%= bookingId %></strong> is coming up soon.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="details">
            <p><strong>Booking ID:</strong> <%= bookingId %></p>
            <p><strong>Scheduled Time:</strong> <%= scheduledTime %></p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> <%= location %></p>
            <p><strong>Contact Person:</strong> <%= contactPerson %> - <%= contactPhone %></p>
        </div>

        <center>
            <a href="<%= bookingUrl %>" class="button">View Booking Details</a>
        </center>

        <p><strong>Next Steps for a Successful <%= reminderType %>:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Ensure all necessary documentation is ready</li>
            <li>Contact the other party for any last-minute updates</li>
            <li>Prepare the cargo/truck as required</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>Need Assistance?</strong></p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need help with the booking, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@iptruck.com">support@iptruck.com</a>.</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br>The IpTruck Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© 2024 IpTruck. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>You received this email because you have an upcoming booking event.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

